<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4578164>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 5. — Cryptopora curiosa Cooper, 1973, Mozambique Channel, Maputo transect, MAINBAZA, stn CP 3132, 101-102 m: A-C, complete specimen (MNHN IB- 2013-40), dorsal view (A), and enlargement of the umbonal part (B) to show details of auriculated deltidial plates and of the outer surface (C) to show radial ornamentation; D-F, inner view of ventral valve (D), and enlargement of posterior part (E) and tilted view (F) to show teeth and dental plates (MNHN IB-2013-41); G-I, inner and oblique views of dorsal valve (MNHN IB-2013-42) to show septum and crura.All SEMs. Scale bars: A, D, G, H, 1 mm; B, C, I, 200 µm; E, F, 500 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4578164/files/figure.png" .

